src:
Siffran visar att Fed gjort ett bra jobb
NEW YORK. Den amerikanska ekonomin fortsätter att visa styrketecken. Trots strejken på General Motors behöll arbetsmarknaden sitt momentum under oktober. Landets centralbank verkar dessutom veta vad man sysslar med.
01 Nov 2019, 15:08 by Frida Wallnor

text:
The figure shows that the Fed has done a good job
NEW YORK. The US economy continues to show strength. Despite the strike on General Motors, the labor market retained its momentum during October. The country's central bank also seems to know what one is doing.
01 Nov 2019, 15:08 by Frida Wallnor
